{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d20c3ac7b3","title":"中央关于伊克昭盟划归华北问题的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1667e31079","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"d20c3ac7b3"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"81a6f20ce7","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"伊盟，即伊克昭盟，今属内蒙古自治区。"},{"id":"432b3a7aad","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"马明方，当时任中共中央西北局副书记。"},{"id":"68e44cf96e","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"奇子祥，即奇天祥，原国民党政府伊克昭盟准格尔旗保安司令，1949年11月5日率部起义。"},{"id":"82da51b7f6","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"傅，指傅作义，原国民党政府军将领，1949年1月率部在北平起义，并对董其武率部在绥远起义做出贡献；当时任中央人民政府委员。董，指董其武，原国民党政府军将领，1949年9月率部在绥远起义；当时任政协第一届全国委员会委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"85a6d00ff6","type":"title","text":"中央关于伊克昭盟划归华北问题的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3"},{"id":"81a6f20ce7","type":"paragraph","text":"西北局，并告华北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3"},{"id":"432b3a7aad","type":"paragraph","text":"成模电悉。关于伊盟归华北问题，原由薄一波同志与马明方同志商定，由马回西北局转达征求你们同意后实施。因马去东北参观，故你们尚不知道此项决定。现据你们来电表示同意，即请径与华北局商定交接事宜，并注意要使交接双方都感满意，并恰当地处理奇子祥问题及伊盟与傅董关系为要","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3"},{"id":"68e44cf96e","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3"},{"id":"82da51b7f6","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3"}],"page":{"id":"e1780737cf","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d20c3ac7b3","start":37,"end":37}}}},"__N_SSG":true}